{"tid":2422403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"輕度智障清潔工被控非法集結 政府精神科醫生指不適合答辯與受審 去年曾因另案判監8個月","createTime":"2021-02-25T07:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T14:32:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"feefafa91f51379047f4ec3f08c64b241a0e96a3","tid":2422403,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"輕度智障清潔工「發仔」被控前年10月在旺角警署外參與非法集結和藏有雷射筆，案件今在西九龍裁判法院再訊。辯方指發仔智商只等於11歲兒童，其智力不適合答辯及受審。裁判官排期至6月2日聆訊處理爭議，將傳召控方和辯方共4名精神科專家作供。<br />\n<br />\n庭上透露，控方索取的兩份政府精神科醫生報告，分別指被告「發仔」不適合答辯及不適合受審；而辯方的兩份私家精神科醫生報告則指，發仔屬僅僅適合答辯或不適合答辯。控方將索取進一步報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/HB6WKE4VVZBQ7BIJRDYIS2XGHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FHB6WKE4VVZBQ7BIJRDYIS2XGHM%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5b983303\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FHB6WKE4VVZBQ7BIJRDYIS2XGHM%2F&h=2616877b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/HB6WKE4VVZBQ7BIJRDYIS2XGHM/</a>"},{"pid":"55095a9c30378177359f605e2d46531f1101e614","tid":2422403,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e324f7a99d477cf34cd1c65e68004cf0096a80","tid":2422403,"uid":30868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:24:53.000Z","msg":"都真係痴撚線， 根本政府精神科都係佢唔適合審落去， 舊年又邊個狗官判佢有罪"},{"pid":"e14a0146ccc91360a86ac4b73b6616f85797bccf","tid":2422403,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:28:11.000Z","msg